text: I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I'm not gonna lie, I ain't stop until we chilling at the top, swerving on the e-way, don't care if I crash in this coupe, shit I'm thinking about too real, might lose my mind in this coupe, can't relapse off these drugs, man, I RP the juice, we was taking off them perks, I pop my last one with you, but I tell you what my day ones ain't trying to find, no recuse, we was playing give and take on that front line with my truth, ay, like who on smoke? We got plenty guns, keep two little savages on S and they gonna get it done, and them hollow tips do surgery, they gonna clip his lungs, it was going down on the set, that's when the shit was fine, I just been balling on these niggas like I'm Kendrick Narn, everyday my birthday, bitches lit, I just turned 21, decorate your block with red tape, phone them, sliding their date, bunch of hollows spinning out the Glock, I been serving fiends all day, out there posted with the gang, nigga, we was taught to get it off the block, it's a hundred bands in the safe, now I got a special taste, Michael Mary jeans, fill them up with knots, I been on my grind there a day, don't believe in taking breaks, I ain't stopping until we chilling at the top, ever since I stepped up in this game, I been a bomb threat, I was in the trenches trying to see a life beyond that, cuz complacent niggas usually die up in they complex, nigga, where I'm from, they turn death into a contest, living by the gun, put all my trust into this compact, my niggas went to war but they ain't get no Vietnam check, lil bro on his head, he tryna make his brains ooze, lil bitch, I'm from the north side where they raise goons, took losses in these streets, she got me singing gang blues, I been a real nigga, before this shit became cool, I'm the type to switch my watch up, every time I change moves, he the type to get excited, cuz he made the shade room, decorate your block of red tape, fold them slide near a date, bunch of hollows spittin' out the Glock, I been serving fiends all day, out there posted with the gang, nigga, we was taught to get it off the block, it's a hundred bands in the safe, now I got a special taste, Michael Mary jeans, fill them up with knots, I been on my grind there a day, don't believe in taking breaks, I ain't stopping until we chilling at the top.
